Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today's stage is Teitan High.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like every high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,how many strange stories will emerge?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees through the one and only truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No case is left unsolved with Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Night... mare...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ghosts are haunting your school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recently, our high school has been experiencing a series of supernatural incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been giving me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, they say that people always see that apparition early in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:02:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it that two years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a student who used to come to school early in the morning died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they say it's the curse of that student.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:10.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two years ago, that's before I enrolled...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, please, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come after school today and check,\Nif it's really the work of a ghost or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let it be, let it be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's either someone playing a prank or a natural phenomenon anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, if that ghost appears early in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it wouldn't appear during class, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As the daughter of renowned detective Kogoro Mouri,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:37.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't just let an absurd rumor go unchecked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, aren't you hall monitoring next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see... you're afraid of going to school early in the morning so you want me to check?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't help it because I don't like ghosts...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get rid of them with your karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What makes you think that karate is going to have any effect on ghosts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:03:58.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I may come up with a hint to at least solve the mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:11.19,Title,,0,0,0,,Teitan High School's Ghost Story\N(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me the guy who's helping us investigate is this kid with the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... my dad wouldn't even show up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a renowned detective can't come to check out such a crazy case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he may not suffice as an aide...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he can at least serve as an assistant to I, the deduction queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:42.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're the last person I'd want\Nto hear that comment from...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are our shoe lockers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a little larger than your elementary school, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:49.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:52.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I went to this school for a little over a year...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll put your shoes in my locker, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, what's with that boy, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that the rumored Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! Isn't he cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Blabber mouths Tashiro and Hidaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say that again! He looks like a miniature Kudo and sure looks cheeky!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonny, don't grow up to be a deduction freak, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.99,0:05:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of your business...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd you bring him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:26.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An assistant for investigation! This glasses kid is pretty sharp, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:28.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Investigation, you mean that ghost scare?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aizawa and Nakamichi of the soccer club!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.77,0:05:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:36.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to be cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, will you stop saying things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, how'd your re-test go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although we were seriously on the brink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,True, very true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that one day you'll run out of bad luck too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you then, but take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you find out who the ghost is, let me in on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... nope, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:06.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Right... if things were the way they were supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:11.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I would be coming to this school, studying, talking of trivial things with my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:14.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And leading a normal high school life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Gin and Vodka...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:19.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If those men in black... didn't force me to drink that strange drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:23.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And if I hadn't shrunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:28.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That woman Bellmot one of them, that disguised herself as Dr. Niide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:33.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Got, away from me just as I was about to corner her in order to get
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:37.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}get my body back to normal again and regain my life as Shinichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:41.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That woman is probably an assassin who was sent out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}to kill Al who had betrayed the organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:47.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I remember her saying back then, that she would give up on going after Au...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:50.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I wonder if I can really believe what she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:50.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all she's a witch that has a thousand faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all she's a witch that has a thousand faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:51.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,,,1\NAfter all she's a witch t hat has a thousand faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all she's a witch t hat has a thousand faces
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all she\s a witch t hat has a thousand faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all she's a witch t hat has a thousand faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's as good as Thief Kid when it comes to disguising herself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,qO - 2\NShe may still be around us disguised as somebody"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and scheming to do something
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Va
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,aati\NWhat the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dr. Niide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh .l heard that since the trial is over
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you returned to your hospital in Aomori...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... I was planning on doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But decided against it. I'm worried about my patients too, so .
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, it:sinot.thatieasyssaying goodbye to you all-either...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you're going to remain being our school doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:31.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I came today to tell the school of my intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch, ow- owl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.56,0:07:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-The real doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Hey?! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey: -Hey?!Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just whatido youithink you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yes... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,7777
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI agent called Jodie told me all about what-happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:57.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She told me that a bad person disguised as me tried to do something bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she was sent back to the States for a while, but it seems that Hikaru
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or her grandmother who accompanied her did not take to the States very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I heard that the bad person revealed herself and fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Jodie asked to return back here to Beikacho!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why are you telling me all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was told to tell only you, because you'd surely be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have Dr. Niide help us with\Nthe ghost investigation too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Ghost investigation...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, let's stat, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wailing storeroom of the gym...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One rainy day, a girl student of the gymnastic club who came here early
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in the morning to prepare for morning ctice... heard a wailing voice
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wailing leaked out of the storeroom where nobody was supposed to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The horrifying sound of someone wailing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:08:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girl got scared and left,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,bringing other people from her club back to the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the wailing had stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the only thing left was this desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the desk of a boy student. Hideaki Hosaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who died mysteriously at this school 2 years ago!
